com.philips.lighting.hue.sdk

Class PHAccessPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.philips.lighting.hue.sdk.PHAccessPoint

  • public class PHAccessPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    The PHAccessPoint abstracts a hue access point. An access point is an entry point to the hue system.
